A quick guide to choosing the best snacks Whether you're looking for the perfect snacks for your next party or you have some serious munchies, you can find everything you need at Walmart. We stock an incredible range of snacks, and with our Every Day Low Prices, you can surprise everyone with the variety of snacks you have in your cupboards. From tasty savory treats to delicious cookies, we have you covered no matter your cravings. Savory snacks There s nothing better than cuddling on your sofa to enjoy a movie with a blanket, a pack of tortilla chips and just a bit of guacamole. At Walmart, we have a wide selection of savory snacks so the entire family can find something to munch on. From potato chips and cheese puffed snacks for those who want to keep it simple to wheat and multigrain snacks for those looking for a healthier alternative, there s a salty snack for anyone. Shop for party mix packs if you want to keep an entire group happy or for individual bags for a quiet night in. Find the perfect dip for your tortilla chips from options that include mild and hot salsa or more sophisticated mixes such as salsa with corn and black beans or Pico de Gallo salsa. Our selection of crackers is ideal for those moments you're looking for a versatile kind of snack that goes well as part of a snack mix or with a platter of assorted sliced cheese. Have some pretzels in your cupboard to go with your beer or with a refreshing cider that you can welcome houseguests with. For a healthier alternative that's still incredibly tasty, look for crisps made from whole grain corn wheat that are available in multiple mouth-watering flavors. Nuts and other healthy snacks If you re looking for a nutritious yet delicious snack that s also packed with energy, nuts are healthy nibbles that you can enjoy at home, at the office, on a commute or even in the outdoors. Our large range of peanuts, cashews, almonds, pistachios, pecans and more makes it possible for you to discover your favorite kind of nuts to enjoy no matter the occasion. Make your own trail mix by combining our delicious raw, nuts with dried cherries, raising, dried cranberries, banana chips and chocolate chips for a customized snack that suits your preferences. Choose your favorite from salted, unsalted or seasoned nuts with flavors such as chili, lime, honey and more. You can opt for dry roasted, honey roasted or smoked peanuts as well. Granola bars are an ideal breakfast for those busy mornings or an energy-packed afternoon snack. Mixing toasted rolled oats with dried fruits, nuts and chocolate chips, granola bars are low in calories yet high in protein. Put your feet up and enjoy a bowl of salted or butter popcorn that only took a couple of minutes to prepare in the microwave. Sunflower seeds are nutritious snacks packed with fibers, and you can enjoy them as salted kernels or covered in flavored coatings.  Snacks for a sweet tooth Classic sandwich cookies, chewy chocolate chip cookies or ginger snaps   there are so many options to choose from when you re looking for a delicious treat to satisfy your sweet tooth. We have everything from fruit snacks and jellies to canned fruit and Pudding so you can find something for each member of the family. Treat yourself to our delicious range of sweets and chocolates for a well-deserved, relaxing break or have them ready in your cupboard for when guests are coming over. If you ve got a sweet tooth, you ll certainly enjoy our range of chocolate bars and tablets. Opt for single portions, or go for our handy sharing bags. Keep your little ones satisfied on a break with a selection of mini-sized treats that are perfect for lunch boxes. Our selection of cookies includes chocolate chip, coconut, caramel, peanuts and so much more so you can have a packet ready for everyone in the family. Prepare a quick, delicious dessert at home with one of our instant pudding and pie fillings that come in a multitude of flavors such as chocolate, vanilla or strawberry to suit all tastes.Show moreElectrode, Comp-117692765, DC-prod-dal1, ENV-prod-a, PROF-PROD, VER-1.16.0, SHA-a61be39c429b9ad89de35da485c799e426355f1c, CID-





